equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column.listOfFilter<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n              <span class=\"token attr-name\">[nzFilterFn]</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>column.filterFn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n              {{ column.name }}\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n          }\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tbody</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        @for (data of filterTable.data; track data) {\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>{{ data.name }}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>{{ data.age }}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">